OL,5, A detective who subjected a child to   
OL,6, "sickening sexual abuse" from the age  
OL,7, of 12, including raping them, has been 
OL,8, jailed for 26 years.                   
OL,10,FStephen Hardy, of Greater Manchester   
OL,11,FPolice (GMP), was convicted of 20      
OL,12,Fsexual abuse offences including six    
OL,13,Fcounts of rape.                        
OL,15,FThe 46-year-old did not show "one iota 
OL,16,Fof remorse" for his behaviour, the     
OL,17,Fsentencing judge said.                 
OL,19,FHe had denied carrying out the offences
OL,20,Fbetween December 2012 and June 2020.   
